src:
Didner & Gerge flaggar ner i Trelleborg
Fondförvaltaren Didner & Gerge har minskat sitt innehav i verkstadsbolaget Trelleborg. Det framgår av ett flaggningsmeddelande från Finansinspektionen.
05 Nov 2019, 14:52 by Di

text:
Didner & Gerge flags down in Trelleborg
The fund manager Didner & Gerge has reduced its holding in the engineering company Trelleborg. This is stated in a flagging announcement from the Swedish Financial Supervisory Authority.
05 Nov 2019, 14:52 by Tue
